query:
SELECT
            u.discord_id,
            u.name,
            u.display_name,
            u.avatar,
            COALESCE (
                ARRAY_AGG ((
                    p.id,
                    p.name,
                    p.community,
                    p.created_at,
                    p.updated_at
                )) FILTER (WHERE p.id IS NOT NULL),
                ARRAY[]::record[]
            ) AS "profiles: Vec<UserProfile>"
        FROM users u
        LEFT JOIN profiles p
            ON p.owner_id = u.id
        WHERE u.name = $1
        GROUP BY
            u.discord_id,
            u.name,
            u.display_name,
            u.avatar
